{
  "stem": "13096.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And like they say, they makes you build your appetite.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we used to take that garlic, you know, that clove of garlic and you know, put it into the bread, like butter, like that to dissolve.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was giving a little flavor to the bread.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then you're giving to my sister like medicine, and she will-- she will live.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Another time, you know, myself, you know, I had a-- a very big ball, which I've got still here the-- the-- the-- the scar.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My arm was very, very swollen, full of pus.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, you know, the only thing to do was to go to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was very, very, very frightened to go to hospital.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know it was going to be the end.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A friend of ours, you know, during the-- from Rhodes Island, she had that the husband that's given her-- and previously from another camp, while they were in quarantine they smuggled there a tiny-- tiny penknife, you know?",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Over the barbed to-- to-- to cut the bread or whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She had this hided.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody knew where she had it hided, this-- this-- this penknife.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we ask her if she can give it to us for a little while.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because another friend, that the one she was very religious and keeping the Shabbat songs and all this, said, don't worry, I'll make the operation-- the operation on you.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I say, OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, you know, she went into the-- into the snow, you know, outside it was snow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She put the penknife, and it was, you know, like disinfectant, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The very very cold, it kills the germs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She came with this penknife, and she cutted my thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if you see-- and it was painful.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
